It’s time to get your car sparkling and support a great cause!

Join STARS Miami, @elcarwash , and @thedemoyafoundation for a Car Wash Bash this Saturday, May 3rd from 10 AM to 2 PM at @sportsgrill on Kendall!

9090 SW 97 ave
Miami Fl 33176

We’re talking good tunes, good people, and good times — all while raising money for our Inclusive Summer Camp program!

Bring your friends, bring your family, and bring those dirty cars — let’s make a difference together, one sud at a time!

Don’t miss it — let’s have some fun and wash for a cause!
